<SLUG> BC-NATO-Kosovo, 2nd Ld-Writethru,0628 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
NATO defense ministers look at possible military action on Kosovo
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with Robertson, Ruehe quotes; EDITS to conform and
TRIMS. &QL; 
 &UR; By SUSANNE M. SCHAFER &QC; 
 &UR; AP Military Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
