talks ... I am very hopeful we will make some good progress,''
Butler told reporters. He did not elaborate.
	   Butler is accompanied by 18 senior U.N. arms experts who are
carrying satellite images, charts and material evidence to back
UNSCOM's position that Iraq is also hiding information on illegal
weapons.
