<HEADLINE>
Wide range of options available, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Wide range of options available, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 10, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   S.A. ThayalanASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

