	   SUNWAY College, with over a decade of educational excellence, is
a good choice for Malaysian students to earn an Australian degree
via its twinning programmes.
	   Besides its twinning programmes with Australian universities -
the Flinders University of South Australia, Victoria University of
Technology and the University of Western Australia - Sunway College
also has similar programmes with universities in other countries.
	   For those interested in pursuing a career in either business or
finance, the Sunway-Flinders twinning programme would be a good
choice.
	   The Victoria University of Technology in Melbourne offers a
Bachelor of Business degree.
	   Intakes are in March and July every year.
	   Students complete their first two years at Sunway and the final
year in Australia.
	   Sunway College's Australian twinning degree programmes have
senior lecturers visiting the college often to interact with
students.
	   For more information, visit Sunway College at 5 Jalan Kolej,
Bandar Sunway, 46150 Petaling Jaya, or call 03-7358622, fax
03-7358633.
	   
