For career in accountancy, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
For career in accountancy, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 10, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
