Filipinos the best varsity debaters, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Filipinos the best varsity debaters, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 10, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
