	   The state-run radio and TV have earned Tk 75.84 crore from
advertisements in 11 months of the outgoing fiscal year till May,
reports APB.
	   Of the total, Bangladesh Television earned Tk 63.61 crore and
Bangladesh Betar Tk 12.23 crore.
	   This was disclosed by State Minister for Information Prof Abu
Sayeed in parliament yesterday in reply to a started question from
Haji Mohammad Selim of Awami League.
	   
