<BODY>
<SLUG> HAND-OF-PROVIDENCE sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Hand of Providence, THE INDEPENDENT
</HEADLINE>
Hand of Providence, THE INDEPENDENT &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
