<HEADLINE>
Offer courses relevant to country's needs, colleges urged, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Offer courses relevant to country's needs, colleges urged, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
