<HEADLINE>
Application to strike off winding-up petition put off, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Application to strike off winding-up petition put off, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
