	   TEN per cent of the 87 graduates of the Taylor's College
American Degree Programme have been placed on the honour roll.
	   These students completed the Malaysian component of the four
semesters of the credit transfer programme.
	   This year's graduating students have been accept ed into
universities in the United States and Australia, as well as into
Universiti Telekom and Universiti Tenaga.
