	   YES, it's true what the other bitches say about me. I do prefer
humans to my kind... even though the humans have treated me rather
shabbily.
	   You see, after giving my former owners six lovely puppies, they
decided to keep only my two boys and send the rest of us away. But
they were ``kind'' enough to pay for my spay, so what can I say...
hurray?
	   Anyway, I'm three years old and they do say I'm loving and
smart, and will make an excellent pet.
