<HEADLINE>
Girls, would you like to work in USA?, NATION
</HEADLINE>
Girls, would you like to work in USA?, NATION &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
   NATION
   THAILAND
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

