Perak draws RM145m investments in two months, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Perak draws RM145m investments in two months, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
