Indian village, and dozens men in Zapatista rebel uniforms patrol
the town's square, some with assault rifles. MEXICO-CHIAPAS. Has
moved. By John Rice. AP Photos CHA101-103, SCC102-104.
	   DOLGENBRODT, Germany _ Prosecutors uncover an arson conspiracy
involving otherwise upstanding citizens who wanted to keep asylum
seekers out _ raising new questions about the breadth of
anti-foreigner sentiment. GERMANY-ARSON PLOT. Expected by 0100 GMT;
trial starts at 0700 GMT. By Paul Geitner. AP Photo FRA103-104 of
June 11.
	   PARIS _ The results of a DNA test on the corpse of legendary
French singer Yves Montand show he did not father a young woman who
for years claimed to be his love child, judicial sources say.
FRANCE-MONTAND. Has moved. By Pierre-Antoine Souchard. AP Photos
PAR110.
	   LOOKING AHEAD: Foreign ministers from United States, Britain,
China, Russia, France, Germany, Japan and Italy meet in London on
Friday to discuss nuclear situation in India and Pakistan.
Scheduled landing of space shuttle from final Mir docking mission
on Friday.
