GMT.
	   By Robert Millward
	   BORDEAUX, France _ This Roberto Baggio spot kick is spot on. The
veteran striker, in just his fourth appearance for Italy since his
wayward shootout kick ended the 1994 World Cup, hits a penalty with
six minutes left Thursday to salvage a 2-2 draw with Chile in the
France '98 opener for both teams.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-Italy-Chile. Has moved.
	   By Piero Valsecchi
