<SLUG> BC-Yen-Dollar </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Dollar higher against yen in Tokyo
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   TOKYO (AP) _ The U.S. dollar was trading at 144.54 yen on the
Tokyo foreign exchange market at 9 a.m. (0000 GMT) Friday, up 2.86
yen from its level of 141.68 yen as of 5 p.m. (0800 GMT) Thursday.
</TEXT>
